text.tspan: The front panel features a 20 x 4 character LCD
display, an encoder knob and a tap button.
Turn the encoder knob to navigate the menu or to
change a parameter, and click it in to select.
Clicking and holding the encoder knob will clear
all steps from the step sequencer.
The tap button is used to simulate a decay event,
i.e. to force cVert to generate a random note
